FBIS4-41499 "drsov123_d_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-123 Daily Report 25 Jun 1994 Regional Issues Dudayev Fails To `Destroy' Armed Opposition Group Dudayev Fails To `Destroy' Armed Opposition Group LD2506090494 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 0700 GMT 25 Jun 94 LD2506090494 Moscow Radio Rossii Network Russian BFN [Text] Armed formations backing Dzokhar Dudayev have made an attempt to destroy a political and military opposition group led by Beslan Gantemirov [former mayor of Groznyy]. This action has failed, says ANI, quoting the press center of Chechnya's interim council. Gantamirov's detachments are in possession of armor as well as firearms. They are stationed in the Urus-Martanovskiy rayon, adjacent to Groznyy.
